Package: tornadovpn-client
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: wireguard, wireguard-tools, resolvconf
Maintainer: SRI DHARANIVEL A M <sridharthehacker@gmail.com>
Description: Official desktop client for the Tornado VPN ecosystem.
 The Tornado VPN Client provides a highly secure, PyQt5 graphical interface 
 built exclusively for connecting to Tornado VPN infrastructure. It features 
 automated WireGuard key exchange, JWT session persistence, and integrated 
 Tor-over-VPN routing capabilities. Developed by Sri Dharanivel A M.
 